JOIN `savsoft_category` ON `savsoft_category`.`cid`=`savsoft_qbank`.`cid`
JOIN `savsoft_level` ON `savsoft_level`.`lid`=`savsoft_qbank`.`lid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_qbank`.`qid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_category`
ORDER BY `cid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_level`
===[took:0]

FROM `savsoft_quiz`
WHERE `quid` = '10'

WHERE `quid` = '10'

JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`result_status` != 'Açık'
ORDER BY `rid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_quiz`
ORDER BY `quid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_group`
ORDER BY `gid` ASC
===[took:0]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_group`
ORDER BY `gid` ASC
===[took:0]

FROM `savsoft_group`
ORDER BY `gid` ASC

SELECT *

SELECT *

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '24'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='1' and quid='6' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='24' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,18,19,20) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,18,19,20)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '6'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '6'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '6'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '1'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '1'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '1' and quid ='6' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='6'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='6'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='6'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1 
===[took:0]

FROM `savsoft_result`

JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '25'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='25'

	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,3,17,26,27,28)

FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC

FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '20'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '20' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '27'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='27' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1 
===[took:0]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC

FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '29'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='29' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '40'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '40' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Active'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Inactive'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_payment`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_payment`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_payment`.`uid`=`savsoft_users`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_payment`.`pid` DESC
 LIMIT 10
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-01-01' and paid_date <='2018-01-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-02-01' and paid_date <='2018-02-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-03-01' and paid_date <='2018-03-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-04-01' and paid_date <='2018-04-01'

select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-06-01' and paid_date <='2018-06-01'

select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-08-01' and paid_date <='2018-08-01'

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '30'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='30' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '30'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '30' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '32'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='32' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '35'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='35' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)

FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3

JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '6'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '6'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '6'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '1'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '1'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '1' and quid ='6' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='6'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='6'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='6'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '37'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='37' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_giris_kontrol`
WHERE `uid` = '4'
AND `session_id` = '997fbc2f40aa395c95155c577c6d148b25f9d718'
AND `ip` = '::1'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Active'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Inactive'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_payment`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_payment`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_payment`.`uid`=`savsoft_users`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_payment`.`pid` DESC
 LIMIT 10
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-01-01' and paid_date <='2018-01-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-02-01' and paid_date <='2018-02-01'

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '39'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='39' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '10' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

JOIN `savsoft_level` ON `savsoft_level`.`lid`=`savsoft_qbank`.`lid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_qbank`.`qid` DESC

WHERE `savsoft_result`.`result_status` != 'Açık'
ORDER BY `rid` DESC

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_giris_kontrol`
WHERE `uid` = '4'
AND `session_id` = '997fbc2f40aa395c95155c577c6d148b25f9d718'
AND `ip` = '::1'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Active'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Inactive'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_payment`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_payment`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_payment`.`uid`=`savsoft_users`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_payment`.`pid` DESC
 LIMIT 10
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-01-01' and paid_date <='2018-01-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-02-01' and paid_date <='2018-02-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-03-01' and paid_date <='2018-03-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-04-01' and paid_date <='2018-04-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-05-01' and paid_date <='2018-05-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-06-01' and paid_date <='2018-06-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-07-01' and paid_date <='2018-07-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-08-01' and paid_date <='2018-08-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-09-01' and paid_date <='2018-09-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-10-01' and paid_date <='2018-10-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-11-01' and paid_date <='2018-11-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-12-01' and paid_date <='2018-12-01'

FROM `savsoft_users`

	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25)

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '40'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='40' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '10' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1 
===[took:0]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '41'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='41' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '10' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '41'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='41' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '10' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '41'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='41' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '10' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_giris_kontrol`
WHERE `uid` = '4'
AND `session_id` = '997fbc2f40aa395c95155c577c6d148b25f9d718'
AND `ip` = '::1'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Active'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Inactive'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_payment`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_payment`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_payment`.`uid`=`savsoft_users`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_payment`.`pid` DESC
 LIMIT 10
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-01-01' and paid_date <='2018-01-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-02-01' and paid_date <='2018-02-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-03-01' and paid_date <='2018-03-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-04-01' and paid_date <='2018-04-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-05-01' and paid_date <='2018-05-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-06-01' and paid_date <='2018-06-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-07-01' and paid_date <='2018-07-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-08-01' and paid_date <='2018-08-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-09-01' and paid_date <='2018-09-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-10-01' and paid_date <='2018-10-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-11-01' and paid_date <='2018-11-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-12-01' and paid_date <='2018-12-01'   
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_qbank`
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_quiz`

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '12'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='10' and quid='7' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='12' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (17,18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,17,18,19,20) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (17,18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,17,18,19,20)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '2'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '2' and quid ='7' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='42' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)

FROM `savsoft_result`

JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`

ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10

FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC

FROM `savsoft_result`

AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '20'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '20' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_giris_kontrol`
WHERE `uid` = '4'
AND `session_id` = '997fbc2f40aa395c95155c577c6d148b25f9d718'
AND `ip` = '::1'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Active'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Inactive'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_payment`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_payment`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_payment`.`uid`=`savsoft_users`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_payment`.`pid` DESC
 LIMIT 10
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-01-01' and paid_date <='2018-01-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-02-01' and paid_date <='2018-02-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-03-01' and paid_date <='2018-03-01'

select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-05-01' and paid_date <='2018-05-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-06-01' and paid_date <='2018-06-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-07-01' and paid_date <='2018-07-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-08-01' and paid_date <='2018-08-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-09-01' and paid_date <='2018-09-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-10-01' and paid_date <='2018-10-01'

FROM `savsoft_result`

JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`result_status` != 'Açık'
ORDER BY `rid` DESC

FROM `savsoft_quiz`
ORDER BY `quid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_group`

===[took:0.001]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '42'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='10' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='42' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,30,18,24,27,25) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (30,18,24,27,25) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,30,18,24,27,25)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '10'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '20'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '20' and quid ='10' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='10'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '44'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='44' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='44' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

UPDATE `savsoft_result` SET `individual_time` = 'NaN'
WHERE `rid` IS NULL
===[took:0]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '44'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='44' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1 
===[took:0]

select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='44' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)

FROM `savsoft_result`

JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10

FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1 
===[took:0]

UPDATE `savsoft_result` SET `individual_time` = 'NaN'
WHERE `rid` IS NULL

	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '45'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='45' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '40'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '40' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '45'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='45' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '40'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '40' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '45'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='45' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '40'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '40' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`result_status` != 'Açık'
ORDER BY `rid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_quiz`
ORDER BY `quid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_group`
ORDER BY `gid` ASC
===[took:0]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_giris_kontrol`
WHERE `uid` = '4'
AND `session_id` = '13c0e74c4ad477aa200fd7669fee421702dffba9'
AND `ip` = '::1'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Active'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Inactive'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_payment`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_payment`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_payment`.`uid`=`savsoft_users`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_payment`.`pid` DESC
 LIMIT 10
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-01-01' and paid_date <='2018-01-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-02-01' and paid_date <='2018-02-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-03-01' and paid_date <='2018-03-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-04-01' and paid_date <='2018-04-01'

select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-06-01' and paid_date <='2018-06-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-07-01' and paid_date <='2018-07-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-08-01' and paid_date <='2018-08-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-09-01' and paid_date <='2018-09-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-10-01' and paid_date <='2018-10-01'

                            where q.cid=cat.cid and lvl.lid=q.lid and q.aktifmi=1 ORDER BY RAND() limit 20

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '47'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='47' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '0'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '0' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_giris_kontrol`
WHERE `uid` = '5'
AND `session_id` = '7ec90431697f5fb7d7e75ed1ae9fea5e6c2d73bb'
AND `ip` = '::1'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`result_status` != 'Açık'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` = '5'
ORDER BY `rid` DESC

FROM `savsoft_quiz`
ORDER BY `quid` DESC

FROM `savsoft_group`
ORDER BY `gid` ASC

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`uid` = '5'
AND `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '14'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='5' and quid='7' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='14' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (17,18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,17,18,19,20) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (17,18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,17,18,19,20)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '5'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '1'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '1' and quid ='7' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1 
===[took:0]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`uid` = '5'
AND `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '14'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='5' and quid='7' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='14' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (17,18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,17,18,19,20) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (17,18,19,20) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,17,18,19,20)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '7'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '5'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '1'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '1' and quid ='7' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='7'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_giris_kontrol`
WHERE `uid` = '4'
AND `session_id` = '2fadadcec08492575812cc22f7735a0aa4320444'
AND `ip` = '::1'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_users`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_kurum` ON `savsoft_users`.`kurum_id`=`savsoft_kurum`.`kurum_id`
JOIN `savsoft_kadro` ON `savsoft_users`.`kadro_id`=`savsoft_kadro`.`kadro_id`
JOIN `iller` ON `savsoft_users`.`il`=`iller`.`il_id`
ORDER BY `savsoft_users`.`uid` DESC
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Active'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
WHERE `user_status` = 'Inactive'
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_payment`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_payment`.`gid`=`savsoft_group`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_payment`.`uid`=`savsoft_users`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_payment`.`pid` DESC
 LIMIT 10
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-01-01' and paid_date <='2018-01-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-02-01' and paid_date <='2018-02-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-03-01' and paid_date <='2018-03-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-04-01' and paid_date <='2018-04-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-05-01' and paid_date <='2018-05-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-06-01' and paid_date <='2018-06-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-07-01' and paid_date <='2018-07-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-08-01' and paid_date <='2018-08-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-09-01' and paid_date <='2018-09-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-10-01' and paid_date <='2018-10-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-11-01' and paid_date <='2018-11-01'   
select * from savsoft_payment where paid_date >='2018-12-01' and paid_date <='2018-12-01'   
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_users`
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_qbank`

FROM `savsoft_quiz`

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
AND `savsoft_result`.`uid` != '4'
AND `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` <= '30'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC
 select * from savsoft_result where score_obtained > '30' and quid ='11' group by score_obtained 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained desc limit 3 
 select * from savsoft_result where quid ='11'  group by score_obtained  order by score_obtained asc limit 1 
===[took:0]

SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_group` ON `savsoft_group`.`gid`=`savsoft_users`.`gid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`rid` = '50'
 select * from savsoft_result where uid='4' and quid='11' 
select * from savsoft_answers  where savsoft_answers.rid='50' 
select * from savsoft_qbank join savsoft_category on savsoft_category.cid=savsoft_qbank.cid join savsoft_level on savsoft_level.lid=savsoft_qbank.lid 
	 where savsoft_qbank.qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_qbank.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28) 
	 
select * from savsoft_options where qid in (40,3,17,26,27,28) order by FIELD(savsoft_options.qid,40,3,17,26,27,28)
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
JOIN `savsoft_users` ON `savsoft_users`.`uid`=`savsoft_result`.`uid`
JOIN `savsoft_quiz` ON `savsoft_quiz`.`quid`=`savsoft_result`.`quid`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
ORDER BY `percentage_obtained` DESC
 LIMIT 10
SELECT *
FROM `savsoft_result`
WHERE `savsoft_result`.`quid` = '11'
GROUP BY `savsoft_result`.`uid`
ORDER BY `savsoft_result`.`score_obtained` DESC

FROM `savsoft_result`
